3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses the impact of BER on QoS, which is a multimedia-related topic. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with optimizing system performance, which falls under the scope of systems and control. 
5. cs.COM (Computers and Society) - Although less likely, the paper may also fall under the scope of computers and society as it discusses the issue of massive demands for higher capacity, which has societal implications.
